ab dbg debugger

augroup configgroup
	autocmd!
	" Disable auto-insertion of comments (http://vim.wikia.com/wiki/Disable_automatic_comment_insertion)
	autocmd FileType * setlocal formatoptions-=c formatoptions-=r formatoptions-=o
